task.summary: * Example application that enables js to java communication using JavaFX and embebbed webview. It may need a revision on how it handles that communication channel, but it works * Taken from https://github.com/lipido/javafxwebview
* Demo udp client * Demo udp server
* Añadido los paquetes basicos * La estructura de directorios * La interfaz del tracker
* Added bittorrent util library from course resources
* Added SQLite lib dependency using maven and added a sqlite connection loader with its proper junit tests
* JMS sender & listener created for multipurpose JMS connections
